Name: Crispy Squab
AttributesDescription: Increases DEF of all Resonators in the team by 50%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: The squab, with crispy skin and tender meat, embodies Huanglong's warm hospitality, making it a must-have dish for welcoming guests and a favorite among visitors from all over the world.
